tively. This research is done free of charge for you, although our researchers will appreciate being mentioned in a Hall of Fame or bug bounty if any. Threats to our security researchers are not acceptable and will be dealt with by our Legal team.\n\nWe look forward to working closely with you to resolve this issue. If you wish to switch to confidential emails, our PGP key can be found at https://fortiguard.com/secresearch-pgpkey.\n\n\nKind regards,\n\nFortinet's FortiGuard Labs.\n\n## Impact\n\nCross-Site Scripting","weakness":{"id":62,"name":"Cross-site Scripting (XSS) - Stored"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[{"id":423520,"file_name":"FG-VD-19-022.txt","expiring_url":"https://hackerone-us-west-2-production-attachments.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/000/423/520/0741a58e99681ffc2212074f7bd7bbbf2d756fc8/FG-VD-19-022.txt?response-content-disposition=attachment%3B%20filename%3D%22FG-VD-19-022.txt%22%3B%20filename%2A%3DUTF-8%27%27FG-VD-19-022.txt\u0026response-content-type=text%2Fplain\u0026X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Credential=ASIAQGK6FURQQIRQPFMU%2F20260429%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260429T093442Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=3600\u0026X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjECgaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJHMEUCIQDcXQw%2BKjgQDHd%2FGPQ6paEVuWbBuM%2FZeCIr4OwLUNW5mAIgajaxd1seALNlR4oLY%2BSWs0RDtdqA6B%2F0l%2BLG0kaMzaEqugUI8f%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FARADGgwwMTM2MTkyNzQ4NDkiDOaFqgYYJ8y8L84BeSqOBaB8woOFlxAnT%2BAbMd6Q%2BA7KnKENRky9Al39SMa0h48dYatFmMN%2FPHZRHOj%2Fcs8Xuh0Say%2BdSuypedVpGNLkyuNrBQA5NV9C6uhJdriImYFLSoTJRrp0hsmk0QaTsplu7%2Bbw%2ByMgH1FIiRm5D9ZemtWIfVelW3lzvYc7YdSWlfPjbpyK43XVmtXSXhxI%2FeH0AdWMgu76a3mfc3eObIafNKr%2Ba%2B04uIH0kpP1lWfvRmkYmgmrUDfu%2BaFMKspfVcyFPkCvMHKe26rgJg4ZJDu7R2d6mEs7jv3Y9rO9Ak9gm4QSUuCOhln25oTFHHHc9%2Bk6f1qAHgqum%2BOLFvFLJpg9NUnNr4Cri8ZwLinOSXuWLThOE8vsvo9JU7%2FQ18eS3sKEz%2B9sVK%2B04Lph%2B3dwqxV4fbO9SPlzx80oLidlVAZb70nDAWUwJqbZN49eHJQU0YrOt%2Ba3ployIjz2IkGzHNlMJTJeJ86hjeYrlccFGsjH41tWPPBDli4GDD